<seg id=1> China Will Speed the Development of Talented Personnel Market System </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency. Sept. 1. Beijing. The CCPC Organization Dept. and Personnel Dept. recently issued a notice, demanding to strengthen construction planning in talented personnel market, to speed up the development of talented personnel market, and to promote a healthy development of talented personnel market. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> The notice points out that the ultimate target of development of talented personnel market is to achieve individual independence in career choice, unit independence in personnel choice, market regulation of supply and demand, excellent social service, sound social security, and to make market play a basic role, under the overall control of the country, in the distribution of talented personnel resources. </seg>
<seg id=4> The short-term goal of fostering and developping talented personnel market is to make in recent 2 or 3 years the keynote policies and laws that talented personnel market needs, to widely set up in big and medium-size cities talented personnel markets, to establish and develop regional talented personnel information network, to support the development of special talented personnel market, and to set up regional talented personnel markets. </seg>
<seg id=5> By 2000, within the scope of the country, we'll set up initially a talented personnel market system with all-clusive functions, sound mechanism, a complete set of laws and regulations, timely guidance, and considerate services. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> The CCPC Organization Department, Personnel Department required organization departments and personnel deparments at all ranks to strengthen the construction and management of personnel market, to strengthen the research and planning of personnel market, to determine the overall layout and implementation steps of personnel market development, take measures suited to local conditions, offer classified guidances, and gradually establish a perfect system of talented personnel markets. </seg>
</p>
